rows.label: bf11300100_0020
rows.name: So you remembered me. I'm touched.

rows.label: bf11300100_0030
rows.name:
A disgusting face like yours is impossible to forget,
believe me.

rows.label: bf11300100_0050
rows.name:
What do you want?
Though I can guess.

rows.label: bf11300100_0060
rows.name: That thing was mine to begin with.

rows.label: bf11300100_0075
rows.name: First, I've got to give you my thanks for this.

rows.label: bf11300100_0080
rows.name: I'm not gonna kill you quickly.

rows.label: bf11300100_0090
rows.name:
I'm gonna make that smug-looking Blade
of yours watch as I carve you up.

rows.label: bf11300100_0100
rows.name: And I'm gonna enjoy watching him return

rows.label: bf11300100_0105
rows.name: to his Core Crystal, full of despair.

rows.label: bf11300100_0110
rows.name:
I'll create a diversion.
You use that chance to get to the others.

rows.label: bf11300100_0130
rows.name:
That guy knows about your power.
He brought mercenaries instead of Blades on purpose.

rows.label: bf11300100_0155
rows.name:
I'll treat you real nice,
right up to the point you die.
